Introduction

OnlyOneOf is a South Korean boy group formed by 8D Entertainment. They made their Korean debut on May 28th, 2019 with 7 members, however, Love terminated his contract with 8D Entertainment, leaving OnlyOneOf a 6 member group.

On January 12, 2022, OnlyOneOf made their Japanese debut with the mini album "OnlyOneOf JAPAN BEST ALBUM".
